import { Button, TextField, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import { Box } from '@mui/system'
import React from 'react'

 const Login = () => {
    return(<>
      <form>
        <Box>
          <Typography>Login</Typography>
          <TextField/>
          <TextField></TextField>
          <Button>Submit</Button>
          <Button>Back To Signup</Button>
        </Box>
      </form>
    </>)
 }

 export default Login
